text: Peter Ďungel (born 6 September 1993) is a Slovak football midfielder who currently plays for Ružomberok in the Fortuna Liga. ==Club career== ===FK Senica=== Ďungel made his Fortuna Liga debut for Senica against FC DAC 1904 Dunajská Streda on 18 February 2018 against DAC Dunajská Streda in a home 0:2 defeat.FK Senica - FC DAC 1904 Dunajská Streda 0:2 18.02.2018, futbalnet.sk ==References== ==External links== * FK Senica official club profile * * Futbalnet profile Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Slovak footballers Category:Slovak expatriate footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:MFK Tatran Liptovský Mikuláš players Category:MŠK Fomat Martin players Category:FK Pohronie players Category:FK Senica players Category:Stal Mielec players Category:MFK Ružomberok players Category:Slovak Super Liga players Category:2.
